The '''Gardner family''', also collectively known as the '''Gardners of [[Hobbiton Hill|the Hill]]''', was the family name taken by the descendants of [[Samwise Gamgee]] and [[Rose Cotton]] in honour of Sam's replanting of [[the Shire]] after the [[War of the Ring]].<ref name="long">{{App|C4}}</ref>

The family, a branch of which were the [[Fairbairn family|Fairbairns of the Towers]], became an important and influential family of [[Shire-hobbits]] in the [[Fourth Age]].<ref>{{App|C}}</ref>

